		<title>三重勒索是什麼? &#124; 剖析勒索軟體IV</title>
		<link>https://treesheeptw.github.io/portfolio/2023/09/%e4%b8%89%e9%87%8d%e5%8b%92%e7%b4%a2%e6%98%af%e4%bb%80%e9%ba%bc-%e5%89%96%e6%9e%90%e5%8b%92%e7%b4%a2%e8%bb%9f%e9%ab%94iv/</link>
